        "content": "<p>It is not quite what you are asking for but I assume you want <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=ContinuousLinearMap.extend#doc\">docs#ContinuousLinearMap.extend</a> and you take the map that maps <code>A</code> to the completion. Can you please say what is exactly your setup? Is the completion known (usually it is L^2 or something similar), what is the operator?</p>",
